lyrics:
[Verse]
мы рабртаем под вечер
время проводя на работе
кубики льда в стирсмане
и опять петя в хлам

[chorus]
петя, петя, петя, мы не друзья, 
петя, петя.
петя, петя, петя, мы не друзья, 
петя, петя.

[Verse]
In a world so vast, where chaos takes its hold
Randomness unfolds, secrets yet untold
Unpredictable paths, where chance is our guide
Adventure by our side, in randomness we abide

[Chorus]
Oh, random, you're our muse, so wild and free
Creating melodies, full of possibility
In the dance of chance, we find our unique flow
Embracing the unknown, as our spirits glow
